      <description>#5 fits the best, but I have the feeling we are not likely to see much more in the way of percentage based anything added in the future; without caps, percentage increases or decreases tend to balloon out of control as numbers increase or they have to be so small to be virtually nonexistant to prevent the ballooning. Percentages also tend to make it harder to provide upgrades in the future.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Realistically, I hope to see some sort of progressive regen added at some point (tick 1 regen X, tick 2 regen X+5, tick 3 regen x+10, tick 4 regen x+15, etc, for some constant rate), combined with increases to the FT caps and regen rates in general.</description>
