      <title>Re: Mana Pool Regeneration</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=clericbalance&amp;message.id=9041#M9041</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;five minute medding, using the same rules developed for health regen:&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;1. you must not be on any hate lists.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;2. the effect ends if you cast a detrimental spell.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;3. your current mana regen with buffs, ft, aa, etc is doubled every minute, compounding.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;so, if your standing around with low buffs, etc, and your regen is only 40ish... minute 2 its now 80, minute 3 its now 160, minute 4 its now 320.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;your on a drogmor, full raid buffs... minute 1 its 108, minute 2 its now 216, minute 3 its now 432, etc.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;next, do the same for health, except times 3 or 4 if needed to make sure even those guys with 15k health get to full in 5 minutes or less.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;that reduces down times, including death, to minimal levels of wait.&amp;nbsp; you can even do something similer for endurance.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
